    {
      "chinese": "布農族的傳統生計，是以山田燒墾為農耕方式。除了農耕之外，狩獵及採集亦是我們獲得糧食的來源。農耕的作物包含了小米、玉米、薯類、豆類等。",
      "ab": "Maca madadaingaz is Bunun qabas ca malkacias quma, nanu’ tu makucia sapuzi’ pinqainsa’ is ludun kaquma. Na nii’ tu mu’haz malkaciat quma, maiza amin ca duma’ kukuzaun nai na minkakaunun, maupas tinqaqanup ciin mincicikmaz kilim is duma’ a kakaunun, uuca sincucuaz a na cias maduq, atipul, hutan, bainu.",
